    {
      "id": "E:note:row514575:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "82 y/o male with PMH CAD s/p CABG [**2152**] redo [**10/2171**] (LIMA-LAD, SVG-O",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row514575#s1",
      "text": "82 y/o male with PMH CAD s/p CABG [**2152**] redo [**10/2171**] (LIMA-LAD, SVG-OM,    SVG-Diag), CHF (EF 51%), and EtOH abuse, s/p a complicated hospital    course at [**Hospital 755**] Hospital including intubation and treatment for DTs    and respiratory distress with both antibiotics and CHF medication,    NSTEMI with Trop 1.5, who was transferred here for cath after    reportedly having had infero-septal as well as apical ischemia induced    on a stress test."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row514575:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "In cath lab, pt became acutely agitated during the procedure after only    1 ves",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row514575#s2",
      "text": "In cath lab, pt became acutely agitated during the procedure after only    1 vessel was able to be intervened upon (SVG-OM) (the plan was for    intervention of his LAD, aborted d/t agitation)."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row514575:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Pt transferred to the CCU for further observation and treatment of his    agitat",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row514575#s3",
      "text": "Pt transferred to the CCU for further observation and treatment of his    agitation."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row514575:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Psych consulted, awaiting arrival.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row514575#s4",
      "text": "Psych consulted, awaiting arrival."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row514575:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "[**Name8 (MD) 54**] MD s thus far, plan    tonight will be treatment of his agit",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row514575#s5",
      "text": "[**Name8 (MD) 54**] MD s thus far, plan    tonight will be treatment of his agitation with haldol, and monitoring    for symptoms of angina as well as DTs."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row514575:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Per Dr. [**Last Name (STitle) 161**], [**First Name3 (LF) **] plan on    interve",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row514575#s6",
      "text": "Per Dr. [**Last Name (STitle) 161**], [**First Name3 (LF) **] plan on    intervention on Thursday if MS resolves."
    },
